# App Launchers
# Run immediately on these phrases - no explanation, no confirmation.
# PowerShell tool (NOT Bash) for Windows. bash for Mac/Linux.

| Phrase | PowerShell Command |
|--------|---------|
| "launch [app name]" | `Start-Process "C:\path\node_modules\.bin\electron.cmd" -ArgumentList "." -WorkingDirectory "C:\path\to\app"` |
| "launch [app name] with build" | `Push-Location "C:\path"; npm run build --silent 2>$null; Pop-Location; Start-Process "C:\path\node_modules\.bin\electron.cmd" -ArgumentList "." -WorkingDirectory "C:\path"` |

