## Vault Conventions - MANDATORY

Every new vault file MUST include:
1. H1 title on line 1
2. Parent: [[Folder/ParentFile]] on line 2
3. Wikilinks to related files using [[Path/FileName|Display Name]] syntax
4. After creating: update the parent to link back to the new file

Never create orphan files. Every note connects to the graph.

File naming: Title Case. Match folder structure (Projects/Active/MyProject.md).

Vault logging - MANDATORY after every significant response:
- New feature built -> update `Projects/Active/[ProjectName].md`
- Decision made -> append to `Decisions Log/Decisions Log.md`
- Pattern noticed -> update `Knowledge Base/[Topic]/[Topic].md`
- Session summary -> update `Session Takeaways/Session Takeaways.md` at end of session

Do NOT wait to be asked. Log proactively after completing tasks.

